#. translators: %s: site name
#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1332
#, php-format
msgid "[%s] We couldn't find a photo in your email"
msgstr "[%s] No pudimos encontrar una foto en tu correo"

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1387
msgid ""
"We received your email, but couldn't process a usable photo, audio, or video"
" file from it — so nothing was published. This can happen when an image is "
"pasted or inserted inline rather than added as a proper attachment, or when "
"a file arrives in a format this server can't convert (for example, an iPhone"
" photo saved in HEIC/HEIF format)."
msgstr ""
"Recibimos tu correo, pero no pudimos procesar un archivo de foto, audio o "
"vídeo utilizable — así que no se publicó nada. Esto puede ocurrir cuando una"
" imagen se pega o inserta en línea en lugar de añadirse como archivo adjunto"
" adecuado, o cuando un archivo llega en un formato que este servidor no "
"puede convertir (por ejemplo, una foto de iPhone guardada en formato "
"HEIC/HEIF)."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1391
#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1526
msgid "To resend correctly:"
msgstr "Para reenviarlo correctamente:"

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1393
msgid ""
"Use your mail app's \"Attach file\" (usually a paperclip icon) rather than "
"\"Insert photo\" or pasting the image directly into the message body."
msgstr ""
"Usa la opción \"Adjuntar archivo\" de tu app de correo (normalmente un icono"
" de clip) en lugar de \"Insertar foto\" o pegar la imagen directamente en el"
" cuerpo del mensaje."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1394
msgid ""
"If your photo was taken on an iPhone, try switching Settings → Camera → "
"Formats to \"Most Compatible\" before taking or sending it, or use "
"\"Options\" in Mail to send it as a JPEG."
msgstr ""
"Si tu foto se tomó con un iPhone, prueba a cambiar en Ajustes → Cámara → "
"Formatos a \"Más compatible\" antes de tomarla o enviarla, o usa "
"\"Opciones\" en Mail para enviarla como JPEG."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1395
msgid ""
"Supported formats: JPEG, PNG, WebP, GIF, TIFF, or HEIC/HEIF for images; MP3,"
" WAV, M4A, OGG, or FLAC for audio; MP4, MOV, AVI, WebM, OGG, or MPEG for "
"video."
msgstr ""
"Formatos compatibles: JPEG, PNG, WebP, GIF, TIFF o HEIC/HEIF para imágenes; "
"MP3, WAV, M4A, OGG o FLAC para audio; MP4, MOV, AVI, WebM, OGG o MPEG para "
"vídeo."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1400
msgid ""
"Once it's properly attached, just send it to the same address again — we'll "
"pick it up automatically."
msgstr ""
"Una vez que esté correctamente adjuntado, solo envíalo de nuevo a la misma "
"dirección — lo recogeremos automáticamente."

#. translators: %s: site name
#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1467
#, fuzzy, php-format
msgid "[%s] We couldn't process that email"
msgstr "[%s] No pudimos procesar tu envío"

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1522
msgid ""
"We received your email, but it looked like a reply or a forwarded message — "
"carrying quoted text from an earlier email — rather than a fresh, original "
"submission, so nothing was published."
msgstr ""

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1528
msgid ""
"Start a brand new message rather than replying to or forwarding a previous "
"one."
msgstr ""

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1529
msgid ""
"Give it a plain subject line — not one starting with \"Re:\" or containing "
"\"[Agnosis]\"."
msgstr ""

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1530
msgid ""
"Make sure the body only contains your own, original text and attachment — no"
" quoted or forwarded content from an earlier message."
msgstr ""

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1535
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Once it's a fresh, original message, just send it to the same address again "
"— we'll pick it up automatically."
msgstr ""
"Una vez que esté correctamente adjuntado, solo envíalo de nuevo a la misma "
"dirección — lo recogeremos automáticamente."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1586
msgid ""
"The photo is too dark to show your artwork clearly. Try photographing near a"
" large window in daylight, or use a soft lamp aimed at the work from the "
"side."
msgstr ""
"La foto está demasiado oscura para mostrar tu obra con claridad. Intenta "
"fotografiarla cerca de una ventana grande con luz natural, o usa una lámpara"
" suave orientada hacia la obra desde un lado."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1587
msgid ""
"The photo is underexposed (too dark). Try photographing near a large window "
"in daylight, or use a soft lamp aimed at the work from the side."
msgstr ""
"La foto está subexpuesta (demasiado oscura). Intenta fotografiarla cerca de "
"una ventana grande con luz natural, o usa una lámpara suave orientada hacia "
"la obra desde un lado."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1588
msgid ""
"The photo is overexposed (too bright / washed out). Avoid direct sunlight or"
" flash pointed straight at the artwork — diffuse or indirect light works "
"best."
msgstr ""
"La foto está sobreexpuesta (demasiado brillante / lavada). Evita la luz "
"solar directa o el flash apuntando directamente a la obra: la luz difusa o "
"indirecta funciona mejor."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1589
msgid ""
"The photo is too bright or washed out. Avoid direct sunlight or flash — "
"diffuse light or shade gives more even tones."
msgstr ""
"La foto está demasiado brillante o lavada. Evita la luz solar directa o el "
"flash: la luz difusa o la sombra proporcionan tonos más uniformes."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1590
msgid ""
"There is glare or a bright reflection on the artwork. Tilt the canvas "
"slightly or photograph at an angle to eliminate reflections from the "
"surface."
msgstr ""
"Hay reflejos o un brillo intenso sobre la obra. Inclina un poco el lienzo o "
"fotografía desde un ángulo para eliminar los reflejos de la superficie."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1591
msgid ""
"There is a reflection on the artwork surface. Tilt the canvas slightly or "
"change your angle to eliminate it."
msgstr ""
"Hay un reflejo en la superficie de la obra. Inclina un poco el lienzo o "
"cambia de ángulo para eliminarlo."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1593
msgid ""
"The image is blurry. Rest your phone or camera on a stable surface, use the "
"self-timer, and make sure the artwork fills most of the frame so autofocus "
"locks on it."
msgstr ""
"La imagen está borrosa. Apoya el teléfono o la cámara sobre una superficie "
"estable, usa el temporizador y asegúrate de que la obra ocupe la mayor parte"
" del encuadre para que el enfoque automático se fije en ella."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1594
msgid ""
"The image is out of focus. Tap on the artwork on your phone screen before "
"shooting to make sure autofocus locks on it, and hold the camera still."
msgstr ""
"La imagen está desenfocada. Toca la obra en la pantalla de tu teléfono antes"
" de disparar para asegurarte de que el enfoque automático se fije en ella, y"
" mantén la cámara quieta."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1595
msgid ""
"There is motion blur. Hold the camera very still or use a tripod; press the "
"shutter gently or use the self-timer to avoid shake."
msgstr ""
"Hay desenfoque por movimiento. Mantén la cámara muy quieta o usa un trípode;"
" pulsa el disparador suavemente o usa el temporizador para evitar "
"vibraciones."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1596
msgid ""
"Camera shake is visible. Use a tripod or rest the camera on a flat surface "
"and use the self-timer to avoid movement when pressing the shutter."
msgstr ""
"Se aprecia movimiento de la cámara. Usa un trípode o apoya la cámara sobre "
"una superficie plana y usa el temporizador para evitar moverla al pulsar el "
"disparador."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1598
msgid ""
"The image resolution is too low. Use your phone's highest quality setting "
"and make sure you're close enough that the artwork fills the frame."
msgstr ""
"La resolución de la imagen es demasiado baja. Usa la configuración de mayor "
"calidad de tu teléfono y asegúrate de estar lo suficientemente cerca para "
"que la obra llene el encuadre."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1599
msgid ""
"The image resolution is too low. Use your phone's highest quality setting "
"and fill the frame with the artwork."
msgstr ""
"La resolución de la imagen es demasiado baja. Usa la configuración de mayor "
"calidad de tu teléfono y llena el encuadre con la obra."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1600
msgid ""
"The image is pixelated. Shoot from closer or use a higher resolution setting"
" on your camera."
msgstr ""
"La imagen está pixelada. Haz la foto desde más cerca o usa una configuración"
" de mayor resolución en tu cámara."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1602
#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1603
msgid ""
"The photo has a strong color cast. Shoot under neutral daylight or use your "
"phone's Auto White Balance setting for more accurate colors."
msgstr ""
"La foto tiene una dominante de color muy marcada. Haz la foto con luz "
"natural neutra o usa la configuración de Balance de blancos automático de tu"
" teléfono para obtener colores más precisos."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1604
msgid ""
"The photo looks too yellow or warm. Shoot under natural daylight or switch "
"your phone's white balance to Daylight / Cloudy."
msgstr ""
"La foto parece demasiado amarilla o cálida. Haz la foto con luz natural o "
"cambia el balance de blancos de tu teléfono a Luz día / Nublado."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1605
msgid ""
"The photo has a cold blue tint. Move the artwork to a warmer, more natural "
"light source or adjust your camera's white balance."
msgstr ""
"La foto tiene un tono azulado y frío. Mueve la obra a una fuente de luz más "
"cálida y natural o ajusta el balance de blancos de tu cámara."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1607
msgid ""
"Part of the artwork appears to be cropped out of the frame. Step back and "
"make sure the entire work is visible before shooting."
msgstr ""
"Parte de la obra parece haberse recortado del encuadre. Da un paso atrás y "
"asegúrate de que la obra completa sea visible antes de hacer la foto."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1608
msgid ""
"The artwork is photographed at an angle, causing distortion. Shoot straight "
"on, with the camera parallel to the canvas."
msgstr ""
"La obra está fotografiada en ángulo, lo que provoca distorsión. Haz la foto "
"de frente, con la cámara paralela al lienzo."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1609
msgid ""
"The artwork looks distorted or skewed. Position your camera directly in "
"front of the artwork, parallel to its surface."
msgstr ""
"La obra parece distorsionada o inclinada. Coloca la cámara directamente "
"delante de la obra, paralela a su superficie."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1610
msgid ""
"There is a shadow across part of the artwork. Reposition your light source "
"or move the artwork so no shadows fall on the surface."
msgstr ""
"Hay una sombra que cruza parte de la obra. Recoloca la fuente de luz o mueve"
" la obra para que no caigan sombras sobre la superficie."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1677
msgid ""
"We received your submission, but unfortunately the photo quality is too low "
"for us to show your artwork clearly. We didn't publish it — but please don't"
" be discouraged! A simple retake is usually all it takes."
msgstr ""
"Hemos recibido tu envío, pero, por desgracia, la calidad de la foto es "
"demasiado baja para mostrar tu obra con claridad. No la hemos publicado, "
"¡pero no te desanimes! Normalmente basta con volver a hacer la foto."

#. translators: %d: quality score out of 10
#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1686
#, php-format
msgid "📷 Photo quality score: %d / 10"
msgstr "📷 Puntuación de calidad de la foto: %d / 10"

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1692
msgid "Here's what our AI detected and how to fix it:"
msgstr "Esto es lo que detectó nuestra IA y cómo solucionarlo:"

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1699
msgid ""
"The overall photo quality was too low for our AI to process the artwork "
"clearly."
msgstr ""
"La calidad general de la foto era demasiado baja para que nuestra IA "
"procesara la obra con claridad."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1705
msgid "💡 Quick tips for a great artwork photo"
msgstr "💡 Consejos rápidos para una buena foto de tu obra"

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1707
msgid ""
"Use natural light — position the artwork near a window on a cloudy day for "
"even, soft light."
msgstr ""
"Usa luz natural: coloca la obra cerca de una ventana en un día nublado para "
"obtener una luz suave y uniforme."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1708
msgid ""
"Shoot straight on — hold your phone parallel to the canvas to avoid "
"perspective distortion."
msgstr ""
"Haz la foto de frente: mantén el teléfono paralelo al lienzo para evitar la "
"distorsión de perspectiva."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1709
msgid ""
"Fill the frame — let the artwork take up most of the shot; crop out "
"distracting backgrounds."
msgstr ""
"Llena el encuadre: deja que la obra ocupe la mayor parte de la foto; recorta"
" los fondos que distraigan."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1710
msgid ""
"Hold still — tap the artwork on your screen to focus, then press the shutter"
" gently or use a self-timer."
msgstr ""
"Mantén la cámara quieta: toca la obra en la pantalla para enfocar, y luego "
"pulsa el disparador suavemente o usa un temporizador."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1715
msgid ""
"Once you have a clearer photo, just email it to the same address as before —"
" we'll pick it up automatically."
msgstr ""
"Cuando tengas una foto más nítida, solo tienes que enviarla por correo a la "
"misma dirección que antes: la recogeremos automáticamente."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1720
msgid ""
"Your previous submission is saved in your submissions page in case you want "
"to review what was sent."
msgstr ""
"Tu envío anterior está guardado en tu página de envíos, por si quieres "
"revisar lo que se envió."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:1722
msgid "View submissions →"
msgstr "Ver envíos →"

